Class AbstractConfigWrapper

java.lang.Object
io.github.ttno1.configvalidation.defaultwrappers.AbstractConfigWrapper
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:

public abstract class AbstractConfigWrapper extends Object implements ConfigWrapper
A ConfigWrapper that gets Object values from some source for a given path.
